OL,3,CWales and Swansea midfielder Joe Allen
OL,4,Cannounces retirement
OL,6,FWales midfielder Joe Allen has
OL,7,Fannounced his retirement from football
OL,8,Fafter his instinct told him he was not
OL,9,Fgoing to reach next year's World Cup.
OL,11,FAllen, who won 77 caps for Wales and
OL,12,Fwas also a member of the 2012 Great
OL,13,FBritain Olympic team, will play his
OL,14,Ffinal game for Swansea on Saturday.
OL,16,FThe 35-year-old ` who played a pivotal
OL,17,Frole as Wales reached the semi-finals
OL,18,Fof Euro 2016 and was named in the
OL,19,Fofficial team of that tournament ` has
OL,20,Fmade over 580 appearances in an 18-
OL,21,Fyear senior career.
