OL,3,CWales and Swansea midfielder Joe Allen
OL,4,Cannounces retirement
OL,6,FAllen started and ended his career at
OL,7,FSwansea and also played for Wrexham,
OL,8,FLiverpool and Stoke.
OL,10,FHe reversed his February 2023 decision
OL,11,Fto retire from international football
OL,12,Fin October citing "unfinished
OL,13,Fbusiness" with Wales, but said ahead
OL,14,Fof his final game against Oxford: "The
OL,15,Ftiming's right. A lot of factors go
OL,16,Finto the decision, but when you get to
OL,17,F35 you're only getting worse.
