OL,3,CWales and Swansea midfielder Joe Allen
OL,4,Cannounces retirement
OL,6,F"I still think I have some value and
OL,7,Fsomething to offer, but there's
OL,8,Fprobably a line I didn't want to cross
OL,9,Fin terms of the level of performance I
OL,10,Fcan give.
OL,12,F"I'm probably right up to that line at
OL,13,Fthe moment. When you couple that with
OL,14,Fthe injuries you accumulate over the
OL,15,Fyears, I'm at that stage where I can't
OL,16,Fpush things any further.
