OL,3,CWales and Swansea midfielder Joe Allen
OL,4,Cannounces retirement
OL,6,F"It (the 2026 World Cup) was a big
OL,7,Fpart of the decision. My instinct told
OL,8,Fme I wasn't going to get there. Or, if
OL,9,FI did get there, it wasn't going to be
OL,10,Fat the level I wanted to be
OL,11,Frepresenting my country at a World Cup.
OL,13,F"So, it certainly made thinking about
OL,14,Fretirement a lot harder, with that on
OL,15,Fthe horizon next summer.
OL,17,F"But, realistically, I didn't quite
OL,18,Ffeel I was going to get there."
