OL,4,Cannounces retirement
OL,6,FPembrokeshire-born Allen broke won
OL,7,Fpromotion into the Premier League at
OL,8,FSwansea in 2011 and helped establish
OL,9,Fthem as a top-flight club, before
OL,10,FBrendan Rodgers signed him for
OL,11,FLiverpool in a #15million deal in 2012.
OL,13,FAllen made over 130 appearances for
OL,14,FLiverpool and was a Premier League,
OL,15,FLeague Cup and Europa League runner-up
OL,16,Fahead of spending six years at Stoke
OL,17,Fand three more at Swansea.
