OL,6,F"A few stand-outs would be the play-
OL,7,Foff final with Swansea, getting
OL,8,Fpromoted to the Premier League, and
OL,9,Fthe first season there," said Allen.
OL,11,F"Also joining a huge and historic club
OL,12,Fin Liverpool and competing at the top
OL,13,Fof the Premier League with some
OL,14,Funbelievable players.
OL,16,F"The Euros in 2016 is the stand-out,
OL,17,Fan amazing summer, but there's been
OL,18,Fmany more."
