OL,3,CWales and Swansea midfielder Joe Allen
OL,4,Cannounces retirement
OL,6,FAs well as Euro 2016, Allen featured
OL,7,Fat Euro 2020 and the 2022 World Cup in
OL,8,FQatar to become one of the few
OL,9,FWelshmen in three major tournaments.
OL,11,FCraig Bellamy, a former teammate,
OL,12,Fpersuaded him to return to the
OL,13,Finternational fold after succeeding
OL,14,FRob Page as Wales manager and Allen
OL,15,Fwould add three more caps to his tally.
OL,17,F"When you see a player like him in
OL,18,Ftraining and the habits he has, you
OL,19,Funderstand why he's had such a great
OL,20,Fcareer," said Bellamy.
